      "message": "I am really reluctant to have hard-coded IP addresses.\nAlexis, please take a look at this review: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/22997/ (which by the way should be merged imho...) and the mechanism to automatically update IP addresses in /etc/hosts.\nWDYT?",
